<p class="intro">This e-commerce app has been completed by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/artem-pokhiliuk/">Artem Pokhiliuk</a> as a training project. It has been made in Laravel framework with embedding a single-page reactive instance of Vue.js for <a href="/products">the page</a> displaying available products.</p>

<p class="intro">The user interface for clients and for admins has been developed. If you want to get access to the admin part, when log in under <strong>a@a</strong> email and with <strong>aaaaaa</strong> password, and product management features will become available.</p>

<p class="intro">The RESTful API with token-based authentication (using Laravel Sanctum) has also been developed for this app. You can download OpenAPI definitions in YAML format <a href="/openapi.yaml">here</a>. A convenient roundup of all existing endpoints and the HTTP methods with examples of requests and responses is below on this page.</p>

<p class="intro">All code is covered with automated tests. You can take a look at them, just like at any other piece of source code, in <a href="https://github.com/Marre-86/manul-shop">Github repo</a>.</p>
